      • addUser

        String addUser(String sfOrg,
               String mainUserID,
               String userID,
               String name,
               KBConfig kbConfig)
        Somewhat of a misdirection, addUser does NOT add a Users record, it must already exist. This method adds the supporting Group, Folder, FolderFolders, and FolderContent, records.
        Parameters:
        sfOrg - The salesforce.com Org or null if this is not a salesforce.com user
        mainUserID - The main users ID, also main group number
        userID - The user's ID
        name - The user's name
        kbConfig - The place to retreive the JDBC connection
        Returns:
        a string prefixed with "SUCCESS:" or "FAILED"
